	   <tr><td colspan=2>I was wondering, is Half Elven Bard a wise race class combo?  I'm planning on starting a bard within the next few months (my mage char needs the attention first though :)) in Qeynos, because I like the area better than Kelethin (too dark, too hilly ect :))  So any thoughs?<br>&nbsp;<br>Andara Lan'Gstom<br>25 Mage<br>&lt;Shadowed Blade&gt;<br><a href="http://members.home.net/shadowedblade/" target=_new>http://members.home.net/shadowedblade/</a><br>TP Server</td></tr>
